name: FTSO AU
description: Providing value to the Flare ecosystem and it's participants.
general: We provide accurate and reliable price feeds to the Songbird & Flare network and a transparent, incentivised, risk-free delegation service. We run observation and validation nodes, as well as underlying chain nodes, to support attestation services. FTSO AU are an active member of the Flare ecosystem.
availability: We use best in class global data centres, our SLA guarantees a Monthly Uptime Percentage of at least 99.99%. Our pricing data is real-time, accurate and robust.
